There are two debian-subdir-only packaging repos,

- https://salsa.debian.org/mpearson/sof-bin-packaging.git
- https://salsa.debian.org/stephanlachnit/sof-bin-packaging.git

which can be built with

	git clone https://salsa.debian.org/mpearson/sof-bin-packaging.git
	git clone -b stable-v1.6 https://github.com/thesofproject/sof-bin.git
	tar -zcf sof-bin_1.6.orig.tar.gz sof-bin
	cd sof-bin
	cp -r ../sof-bin-packaging/debian .
	debuild -us -uc

and one debian-branch-upstream-merged

- https://github.com/barak/sof-bin.git

which can be built with

	fakeroot debian/rules binary

All are based on https://github.com/thesofproject/sof-bin branch stable-v1.6
